Understanding both the
capabilities and limitations

00:02:13.949 --> 00:02:16.560
of the medium we work
in on a day to day basis

00:02:16.560 --> 00:02:19.830
will help you take the next
important step towards mastery.

00:02:19.830 --> 00:02:22.290
